name: Savio Rebelo
text: Excellent lobster sandwich.  The staff and manager are excellent.  I had a problem with my gift card, and Jose, the manager, went over and beyond to help resolve the issue.  Great food and excellent service.

name: Diana Park-Alford
text: Had a great experience with a korean bbq sandwich.  Ordered the small for just about 5$. It was flavorful with coleslaw and spicy sriracha sauce. Hubby ordered a lobster salad roll meal and it was great.
